{"about_the_game":"Misao - 2024 HD Remaster is a remastered version of &quot;&quot;Misao: Definitive Edition&quot;&quot; (released in 2017). Not only have the graphics, user interface, and presentation been redone and updated for HD resolutions, new content has also been added, giving it a fresh feel.<br><br>This is a horror-adventure game that tells the story of the missing girl Misao. Explore a ghastly school pulled into another world, and seek the truth of what happened to your classmate.<br><br><i>(When launching the game, you can also choose to play &quot;&quot;Misao: Definitive Edition.&quot;&quot;)</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691450/extras/EN7f8s3-zepvc.gif?t=1735191987\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Summary</h2><br>The quiet, plain, and reclusive Misao was often the target of bullies.<br>And three months ago, she suddenly went missing.<br>Ever since that day, there have been all kinds of unnatural events around campus.<br>Rumor has it that it's Misao's &quot;&quot;curse&quot;&quot;...<br>And when the school transforms into a terrifying and otherworldly place, that rumor is proven true.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691450/extras/02.gif?t=1735191987\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Colorful Cast of Characters</h2><br>Your classmates, trapped in the Otherworld, are on the run from all kinds of paranormal dangers. In these fearful circumstances, they may reveal their connections to Misao.<br>In addition, some apparent residents of the Otherworld may help you out as well...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691450/extras/misao_Steam_character_EN.png?t=1735191987\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Evil Forces at Every Turn</h2><br>The Otherworld is filled with violent spirits and deathtraps. But why could this be...?<br>Don't assume you're safe; they'll descend upon you 